  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'The Fountain of Time can send you back safely?


      That really
      is good news.'
    nextOption: But I can't go anywhere without a body...
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Today is definitely your lucky day then.


      At the top of
      that big pyramid behind me is a Body-Matic 2000!

'
    nextOption: A What?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'It used to be used for creating temporary bodies to test the soul
      binding process.


      We haven''t needed to do that for millenia though.

'
    nextOption: Does It Still Work?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'I have no idea.


      Go to the top of the pyramid and see if
      you can get a body from the Body-Matic 2000.'
    nextOption: Thanks, I'll try anything at this point...
